# Generated PSV data headers — baked output of the loaded project (meshes,
# rig, sprites, HUD, audio, node logic). Regenerated on every editor export.
# Tracking them churned the repo, OOM'd pushes, and shipped project IP
# (pokemon_arena assets) into the public tree. Kept on disk for local builds;
# regenerate by exporting from the editor.
